
http://www-01.ibm.com/support/docview.wss?uid=swg27025142
this tool is used create a local repo with the versions and pplications that you need

install steps:
https://www-01.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/SSDV2W_1.7.3/com.ibm.cic.commandline.doc/topics/t_pu_console_install.html

Assumption:
we have IM installed already.

In IM add the repo for PU:
http://www.ibm.com/software/repositorymanager/com.ibm.cic.packagingUtility
you will need an IBM for this location.


After install 
https://www-01.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/SSDV2W_1.7.3/com.ibm.cic.auth.ui.doc/topics/c_managing_packages.html



Or we can use imcl tool to install PU. 
You can find that in the tools directory of your IM installation.

./imcl -c
